# Development Workflow

## Running Locally

- `bun dev` or `npm run dev` - Start the development server using Vinxi
- `bun sst:dev` or `npm run sst:dev` - Start the SST development environment

## Deployment

- `bun sst:staging` or `npm run sst:staging` - Deploy to staging environment
- `bun sst:main` or `npm run sst:main` - Deploy to production environment

## File Structure Conventions

- New page components should be added to [src/components/pages/](mdc:src/components/pages)
- Reusable UI components should be added to [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui)
- Shared components used across pages should be added to [src/components/shared/](mdc:src/components/shared)
- Backend logic should be organized in the [convex/](mdc:convex) directory based on user type

## Testing

- `bun test` or `npm run test` - Run tests using Vitest
